From 1140f1ab18f009cb00ef3eb3df749cdaecb3dbbf Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Claude <noreply@anthropic.com>
Date: Tue, 7 Jul 2026 16:48:51 +0000
Subject: [PATCH] Add chore copying, history/calendar, penalty chores, remarks,
 and redemption reset

- Copy all chores from one kid to another in Parent Zone (skips duplicates by title)
- Kid dashboard gains a History tab with a date picker showing that day's earned/spent/net score plus a running balance through that date
- Chores support negative star values (penalty/demerit chores) and per-chore remarks, editable from Parent Zone
- Parent Zone shows redemption history per kid with a Reset button to undo a claimed reward and restore its stars
